title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map.
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table that contains highlights or maps.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.

Expected behavior: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions being thrown.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions being thrown.
